OL,3,CGardeners in Sussex prepare to welcome
OL,4,Cvisitors for National Garden Scheme
OL,6,FWATCH: ITV News Meridian's report is
OL,7,Fby Charlie Wilkins
OL,9,FGardens big and small are being
OL,10,Fprepared to open for the annual
OL,11,FNational Garden Scheme.
OL,13,FAround 3,500 private gardens are open
OL,14,Fto the public, nationally. 140 in
OL,15,FSussex alone. The NDS, which has been
OL,16,Frunning for nearly a century was
OL,17,Fstarted to raise funds for district
OL,18,Fnursing.
