OL,3,CGardeners in Sussex prepare to welcome
OL,4,Cvisitors for National Garden Scheme
OL,6,FSeaford gardener, Geoff Stonebanks,
OL,7,Fhas welcomed 23,000 visitors to his
OL,8,Fgarden, Driftwood. Geoff will open his
OL,9,Fgarden, by appointment, from the 1st
OL,10,Fof June. Other gardens will open later
OL,11,Fin the season.
OL,13,FLast year, the scheme raised nearly #4
OL,14,FMillion for various charities,
OL,15,Fincluding Macmillan Cancer Support and
OL,16,FMarie Curie.
